<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<title>할인쿠폰 선택 - GS Retail</title>
	<meta name="viewport" content="user-scalable=no, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, width=device-width, target-densitydpi=medium-dpi" />
	<meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no,address=no,email=no" />
	<meta name="description" contents=""/>
	<meta name="keywords" contents=""/>
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.ico">
	<link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="../images/favicon/favicon.png">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
	<script src="../../js/jquery-1.12.4.min.js"></script>
	<script src="../../js/common.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
	<!-- fullpop :: 할인쿠폰 선택 -->
	<div id="pop01" class="fullPop">
		<h1>할인쿠폰 선택</h1>
		<div class="popCon">
			<ul class="couponList line">
				<li>
					<strong>상품권</strong>
					<div class="selectList">
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="radio" id="coupon01-01" name="coupon01">
							<label for="coupon01-01">적용안함</label>
						</span>
						<span class="checkForm formPrice">
							<input type="radio" id="coupon01-02" name="coupon01" checked="">
							<label for="coupon01-02">3,000원 할인쿠폰</label>
						</span>
					</div>
				</li>
				<li>
					<strong>장바구니할인 쿠폰</strong>
					<div class="selectList">
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="radio" id="coupon02-01" name="coupon02">
							<label for="coupon02-01">적용안함</label>
						</span>
						<span class="checkForm formPrice">
							<input type="radio" id="coupon02-02" name="coupon02" checked="">
							<label for="coupon02-02">장바구니 3,000원 쿠폰</label>
						</span>
						<span class="checkForm">
							<input type="radio" id="coupon02-03" name="coupon02">
							<label for="coupon02-03">장바구니 2,000원 쿠폰</label>
						</span>
					</div>
				</li>
			</ul>
			<ul class="notiInfo">
				<li>할인쿠폰과 장바구니 쿠폰은 중복해서 적용할 수 없습니다.</li>
				<li>할인쿠폰 변경 시 적립금과 결제수단 설정이 초기화 됩니다.</li>
			</ul>
			<div class="btnFixed">
				<div class="btnPrss">
					<button type="button" class="btnTP active">쿠폰적용</button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<button type="button" class="btnClose">팝업 닫기</button>
	</div>
	<!-- //fullpop :: 할인쿠폰 선택 -->
</body>
</html>

